code: public void testGenerateSecureNCName() {     int previousLength = 0.     for (int bytes = randomIntBetween(1, 10). bytes <= 30. bytes += 5) {         final String name = SamlUtils.generateSecureNCName(bytes).         // See: http://www.datypic.com/sc/xsd/t-xsd_NCName.html         assertThat(name, matchesPattern("^[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_.-]*$")).         assertThat(name.length(), greaterThanOrEqualTo(bytes)).         assertThat(name.length(), greaterThan(previousLength)).         previousLength = name.length().     } }
